text: Elisabeth Ostermeyer (born 2 April 1929) is a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nuremberg
